 summarized in our Source article. We provide a set of permissively licensed,
 open source, cross platform software components in the Avogadro 2 libraries,
 along with an end-user application with full source code, and binaries.
 This package includes the library that provides access to input/output file
 formats of various quantum chemistry program packages.

